data.text:
180 Gram Music On Vinyl Import

The debut album from Son Doobie, Tomahawk Funk, & DJ Ralph M, with production by DJ Muggs, DJ Lethal, and T-Ray. As part of the Soul Assassins collective, Funkdoobiest brought the party and comedy to compliment the harder edge drinkin' and brawlin' sound of House of Pain and the weed smokin' street tales of the originators' Cypress Hill.
